Package: owidR
Type: Package
Title: A Package for Importing Data from Our World in Data
Version: 1.0.0
Author: Piers York
Maintainer: Piers York <piersyork@gmail.com>
Description: Scrapes data from the Our World in Data website to offer easy to use functions for searching for datasets and downloading them into R.
URL: <https://github.com/piersyork/owidR>,
        https://github.com/owid/covid-19-data/,
        <https://ourworldindata.org/>
